name: Camp HalfBlood
story: Welcome to Camp halfblood young demigod.
nav: Press 1 to go to cabin Zeus, Press 2 to go to cabin Poseidon and Press 3 to go to Cabin Hades

name: North Woods
story: The most dangerous part of camp. A minotaur attacks and kill you.

story: Welcome, child of Zeus. There are very few of you since the pact.
